    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Use the two argument for of <code>Collections.sort</code>. You will want a suitable <code>Comparator</code> that treats case appropriate (i.e. does lexical, not UTF16 ordering), such as that obtainable through <code>java.text.Collator.getInstance</code>.</p>\n"
